             were indicted for <rs id="t17980523-41-off221" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t17980523-41-off221" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17980523-41-off221" type="offenceSubcategory" value="grandLarceny"></interp>
               feloniously stealing, on the <rs id="t17980523-41-cd222" type="crimeDate">15th of May</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t17980523-41-off221 t17980523-41-cd222"></join>, fifty-five pieces of printed cotton cloth, containing 1500 yards, value 150l.
            </rs> the property of 
               
                  <persName id="t17980523-41-victim387" type="victimName">Thomas Jackson<interp inst="t17980523-41-victim387" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
               
